  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Designing Core Components**\n\nI\'m now focusing on implementing the core components. My thoughts revolve around crafting a highly professional and feature-rich user experience. I\'ve begun designing three modular React components within `/src/components/`, with the aim of creating a strong foundational structure. I\'m keen on establishing robust, flexible components.\n\n\n**Developing the Worship Form**\n\nI\'m currently immersed in the `/src/components/WorshipForm.tsx` component. It\'s taking shape with sections for greetings, worship order, announcements, and checklists. I\'m prioritizing user-friendliness with quick greeting templates and dynamic lists. The announcements section will feature an Instagram-style preview! Export tools for KakaoTalk and design platforms are also in development.\n\n\n**Visualizing UI Components**\n\nI\'m now visualizing the user interface components. I am considering the `/src/components/DesignGuideView.tsx` file first, imagining a rich right-hand pane with pastel boxes. I\'m focusing on color palette cards that allow instant HEX code copying and a font guide to explain the appeal of trendy fonts. I\'m also planning \"How to make this on Canva/Miricanvas\" instructions. I want the design to be really great. I\'m imagining a phone screen preview with color schemes, fonts, and structured elements.\n\n\n"
    thinking_duration {
